@oscarriddle 
I referenced the build process in the official [dockerfile](https://github.com/tensorflow/serving/blob/master/tensorflow_serving/tools/docker/Dockerfile.devel-gpu) and successfully compiled tf_serving, tensorrt, and cuda together. The original tf_serving is inferred on the CPU. In this way, it can be inferred on the GPU. Whether multi-machine multi-card can be inferred is still under study.
Thanks
